âœ… Step-by-step Setup

1. Initialize the Project

npx create-react-app movie-app
cd movie-app
npm install axios react-router-dom

2. Set Up TMDb API

Create .env in root:

REACT_APP_TMDB_API_KEY=your_tmdb_api_key


